Title: Ladies Rotary Aquaspeed Swiss Made bracelet watch ALB90086/C/04
Description: chapelle_jewellery Visit our eBay Shop Add us to your Favourites list > Subscribe to our Newsletter > About Chapelle Delivery The Chapelle Guarantee Ladies Rotary Aquaspeed Swiss Made bracelet watch ALB90086/C/04 RRP £339.00 Now £195.00 Description This ladies Rotary Aquaspeed watch has a beautifully sophisticated yet stylish design and represents excellent quality and craftsmanship. This Swiss Made Aquaspeed model combines a stainless steel bracelet and round dial with a crystal set bezel for a touch of luxury and sparkle. The stainless steel bracelet features matte and polished sections for a lovely contrast in finish and it is secured by a push button clasp that fits seamlessly in to the design. The bracelet leads up to the stainless steel casing which houses the round black dial. White and silver coloured batons clearly mark the hours and stand out against the black dial colour. Three smaller dials show the chronograph function in action and this is controlled using the buttons on either side of the winder. This Rotary Aquaspeed model is 70m water resistant and there is a date window at the four o’clock position. We are authorised stockists of Rotary Aqauspeed watches and each one is sold in the official, branded Aquaspeed presentation box and is supplied with a lifetime Rotary warranty.
